title: The Entire Cosmos in the Parable of the Sower
description:
We look at the Parable of the Sower as a meta-parable which gives us the very structure of meaning making and an image of how the worold lays itself out. 

Boston Event. 
https://thesymbolicworld.com/event/faith-art-and-symbolism-boston-talk/

Clips Channel:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCObI9A-XPP3KD3Fc3MnzOuw

The outro to my videos was written by Matthew Wilkinson

My website designers,  Anomalist Design: https://www.anomalistdesign.com/

The music at the opening is Russian Eastern Overture, by Rimsky Korsakov.
